OL,2,MThe Hidden Maths of Knitting
OL,4,CAlison Kiddle
OL,5,CFri 13:00-13:40
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GWhen someone mentions knitting, it’s
OL,9,Gunlikely that the first word to spring
OL,10,Gto mind is “mathematics”, but it turns
OL,11,Gout that fibre arts such as knitting
OL,12,Gand crochet have strands of
OL,13,Gmathematics woven into their very
OL,14,Gfabric. This talk is a journey through
OL,15,Gthe history, geometry and topology of
OL,16,Gknitting. Learn how crochet allowed us
OL,17,Gto visualise complex mathematical
OL,18,Gsurfaces long before they could be
OL,19,Gstudied with 3D computer models.
OL,20,GDiscover the careful computations
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
